Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.49,0:22:34.70,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6\be10}気持ちなクスブリ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.87,0:22:38.50,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6\be10}ココロの大地熱く
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.87,0:22:43.34,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6\be10}自然発火的に
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.71,0:22:46.76,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6\be10}メラメラ　炎上
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.84,0:22:50.68,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6\be10}恋に焦がれてゆくの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.72,0:22:53.81,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6\be10}天にも登る
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.85,0:22:56.68,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6\be10}ねぇ　夢心地いい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.72,0:23:01.23,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6\be10}浮ついている台風は
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.27,0:23:05.53,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6\be10}誰にも止められない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.90,0:23:08.95,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6\be10}Water Wind LandにFire
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.99,0:23:11.78,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6\be10}混ぜて Special でしょ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.99,0:23:14.95,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6\be10}ループループしてく心情
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.99,0:23:18.08,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6\be10}まさに森羅万象でしょ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.08,0:23:24.13,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6\be10}Happyの雨が止まらないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.17,0:23:29.88,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6\be10}Never End 永遠のUnity
