Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.49,0:22:34.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6\be10}心情煩躁的猶如煙熏火燎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.87,0:22:38.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6\be10}心靈的大地如火燎原
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.87,0:22:43.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6\be10}彷彿如自燃一般
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.71,0:22:46.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6\be10}熊熊燃燒 火焰飛舞
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.84,0:22:50.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6\be10}渴求著炙熱的戀愛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.72,0:22:53.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6\be10}登上天空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.85,0:22:56.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6\be10}吶 美好的夢境裡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.72,0:23:01.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6\be10}呼嘯而來的颱風
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.27,0:23:05.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6\be10}誰也阻擋不了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.90,0:23:08.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6\be10}水 風 大地上的火焰
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.99,0:23:11.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6\be10}混合起來 很Special吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.99,0:23:14.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6\be10}轉來轉去的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.99,0:23:18.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6\be10}正如森羅萬象一般
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.08,0:23:24.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6\be10}快樂的雨兒停不下來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.17,0:23:29.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6\be10}Never End 永遠的樂園
